parameters.name: OutputType
parameters.description: The output type of the exported definition file. Valid values are JSON and YAML.

parameters.name: Specification
parameters.description: The version of the API specification to use. OAS30, for OpenAPI 3.0, is the only supported value.

nested_items.name: body
nested_items.description: Represents an exported definition of an API in a particular output format, for example, YAML. The API is serialized to the requested specification, for example, OpenAPI 3.0.
